txt.en: Looking into the satchel you see several documents written in the Black Speech. You cannot read what they say, but believe if you brought them to the Rangers at Tinnudir they may be able to translate them.
'Interesting. It will take some time to go through this, as I can sense evil on most of the documents, and it is all written in the tongue of the Enemy.'
'Why Tham Ornen? What connexion to Angmar does that place hold?'
Tham Ornen has been occupied by forces from Angmar. What value they see in the ruins is unknown.
The Rangers are at Tinnudir, south-west of Tham Ornen.\n\nOne of the Rangers will be eager to examine the satchel and determine what its contents mean.
Gúrhebnir is at Tinnudir, south west of Tham Ornen.\n\nGúrhebnir will be eager to examine the satchel and what its contents mean.
